01:36.000 --> 01:37.560
<i>Or so we thought...</i>

01:37.640 --> 01:41.440
<i>What we didn't know was that fate</i>
<i>had many surprises in store for us.</i>

01:45.760 --> 01:47.600
-Let's go!
-Quickly!

01:49.440 --> 01:51.320
Argentina awaits.

01:51.400 --> 01:54.440
-[both laughing]
Come on!

01:56.040 --> 01:57.080
You've never been on a ship.

01:57.160 --> 01:59.840
-[Pedro] You thought you'd get away?
-[Gimena gasps]

01:59.920 --> 02:02.800
Don't you dare move.
This is between Gimena and me.

02:03.440 --> 02:05.640
-She never wants to see you again.
-Let her tell me that.

02:05.720 --> 02:07.800
If you shout, I swear I'll kill you.

02:07.880 --> 02:10.039
Calm down, I'm begging you.

02:10.120 --> 02:12.600
[Pedro] I will when you tell your friend
you're coming with me.

02:13.840 --> 02:16.520
-She's not going with you.
-She'll do as I say!

02:16.600 --> 02:18.920
Otherwise, first I'll kill her, then you.

02:19.000 --> 02:22.920
Fine, I'll do whatever you want,
but put the gun down, okay?

02:29.000 --> 02:30.040
[yells]

02:31.440 --> 02:32.840
[both grunt]

02:37.640 --> 02:39.440
[Alba grunting]

02:43.280 --> 02:45.120
[breathing heavily]

02:50.160 --> 02:53.400
Gimena, no, please...

02:54.000 --> 02:55.360
[softly] Look at me.

02:56.160 --> 02:57.720
[Alba] You shouldn't have been here.

02:57.800 --> 03:00.480
I shouldn't have brought you.
I'm sorry.

03:00.560 --> 03:03.520
-Shh... It was our dream.
-It <i>is</i> our dream.

03:04.840 --> 03:07.920
-It still is. Yes.
-Free women.

03:10.640 --> 03:12.320
[sobbing]

03:21.520 --> 03:23.600
[thunder rumbling]

03:40.960 --> 03:44.080
[Beltrán] So you were in the street
with two bodies,

03:44.160 --> 03:46.240
but you had nothing to do with it.

03:48.840 --> 03:50.120
[clears throat]

03:50.200 --> 03:53.680
-Why should I believe you?
-Because I'm telling the truth.

03:53.760 --> 03:59.000
Alba Romero, 25.
Priors for theft and fraud...

03:59.080 --> 04:00.640
and now murder.

04:01.200 --> 04:03.840
Do you know what happens to murderers?

04:04.920 --> 04:07.280
-The garrote.
-[sobbing]

04:08.240 --> 04:10.240
Unless they cooperate with us.

04:18.240 --> 04:19.079
How?

04:19.880 --> 04:21.839
By doing what you do best...

04:24.000 --> 04:25.240
stealing.

04:26.840 --> 04:30.240
But this time, for me. What do you say?

